ue": "Hinge at hips, squeeze glutes at top, cable between legs", "substitution": "Dumbbell RDL"}, {"name": "Leg Extension", "exercise_library_id": null, "in_library": false, "sets": 3, "reps": 12, "rest_seconds": 60, "weight_guidance": "Moderate, RPE 7-8", "equipment": "Machine", "body_part": "Legs", "primary_muscle": "Quadriceps", "secondary_muscles": [], "difficulty": "intermediate", "form_cue": "Full contraction, slow negative", "substitution": "Sissy Squat"}, {"name": "Seated Calf Raise", "exercise_library_id": null, "in_library": false, "sets": 4, "reps": 15, "rest_seconds": 60, "weight_guidance": "Moderate, RPE 7-8", "equipment": "Machine", "body_part": "Legs", "primary_muscle": "Soleus", "secondary_muscles": ["Calves"], "difficulty": "intermediate", "form_cue": "Full ROM, constant tension", "substitution": "Standing Calf Raise"}]}]'::jsonb,
    'Beach Body Ready',
    'Beach Body Ready - 4w 5x/wk',
    'Medium',
    false,
    'A 12-week aesthetic hypertrophy program designed to build a lean, muscular beach physique. 5-day split targeting chest/back, shoulders/arms, legs, upper body, and glute/ham emphasis. Includes strategic deload weeks and phases from foundation building to metabolic shredding.',
    'Hypertrophy/Muscle Building'
FROM program_variants pv
JOIN branded_programs bp ON bp.id = pv.base_program_id
WHERE bp.name = 'Beach Body Ready'
  AND pv.duration_weeks = 4
  AND pv.sessions_per_week = 5
ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;

